    "If not feasible, the models are optimized and new policies are generated.",
    "The network maintenance personnel are also notified if some actions require manual intervention such as hardware repair.",
    "The physical network provides feedback on the healing results, and the NDT continues to optimize the models to further improve healing strategies.",
